---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="About Rob Sapping - Full Stack Developer, Software Engineer, Automation Engineer & DevOps Enthusiast"
  description="Learn about Rob Sapping's journey in software engineering and DevOps. Experienced professional sharing insights on technology, career development, and industry best practices."
>
  <div class="about-container">
    <div class="about-header">
      <h1>About Me</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Software Engineer & DevOps Enthusiast</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-content">
      <section class="intro">
        <h2>Hello! I'm Rob Sapping</h2>
        <p>
          I'm a passionate software engineer with a deep interest in DevOps practices, 
          infrastructure automation, and helping others navigate the tech industry. 
          Through this blog, I share practical insights, tutorials, and career advice 
          based on my experiences in software development and DevOps.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="expertise">
        <h2>Areas of Expertise</h2>
        <div class="skills-grid">
          <div class="skill-category">
            <h3>Software Engineering</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Full-stack development</li>
              <li>API design and development</li>
              <li>Code review and best practices</li>
              <li>Testing strategies</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="skill-category">
            <h3>DevOps & Infrastructure</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>CI/CD pipeline design</li>
              <li>Infrastructure as Code (IaC)</li>
              <li>Container orchestration</li>
              <li>Cloud platforms (AWS, Azure, GCP)</li>
              <li>Monitoring and observability</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="skill-category">
            <h3>Quality & Automation (SDET)</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Testing and automation at scale</li>
              <li>Designing test frameworks</li>
              <li>CI integration and Playwright/Cypress</li>
              <li>Strategies for reliable releases</li>
              <li>Continuous testing practices</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="skill-category">
            <h3>Leading Projects & Teams (PM Perspective)</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Agile execution and roadmap planning</li>
              <li>Metrics and stakeholder management</li>
              <li>Driving software delivery through people</li>
              <li>Individual contributor to program lead transition</li>
              <li>Process optimization and team leadership</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="skill-category">
            <h3>Career Development</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Technical interview preparation</li>
              <li>Job search strategies</li>
              <li>Professional networking</li>
              <li>Industry trend analysis</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mission">
        <h2>Why I Write</h2>
        <p>
          I believe in the power of knowledge sharing and community learning. 
          This blog serves as both a personal learning journal and a resource 
          for others navigating similar paths in technology. Whether you're 
          just starting your career or looking to level up your skills, 
          I hope you find value in the content I share.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="connect">
        <h2>Let's Connect</h2>
        <p>
          I'm always interested in connecting with fellow developers, DevOps engineers, 
          and anyone passionate about technology. Feel free to reach out!
        </p>
        
        <div class="social-links">
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/rsapping" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link linkedin">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/>
            </svg>
            LinkedIn
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    .about-container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    .about-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .about-header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: #333;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: #666;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    .about-content section {
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .about-content h2 {
      color: #333;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #007acc;
      padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .about-content p {
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #555;
    }

    .skills-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .skill-category {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border-left: 4px solid #007acc;
    }

    .skill-category h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #333;
    }

    .skill-category ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .skill-category li {
      padding: 0.25rem 0;
      color: #555;
    }

    .skill-category li:before {
      content: "âœ“ ";
      color: #007acc;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .social-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .social-link {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      background: #007acc;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .social-link:hover {
      background: #005a9e;
    }

    .social-link.email {
      background: #6c757d;
    }

    .social-link.email:hover {
      background: #545b62;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .about-header h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }
      
      .skills-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      
      .social-links {
        flex-direction: column;
      }
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>